00:55:47.930 --> 00:55:51.900
CHOP about what we can sustain. But I think that is

925
00:55:51.930 --> 00:55:55.300
the question. I think that's the key question, and I think there's two issues, one

926
00:55:55.330 --> 00:55:59.110
of which is what you mentioned in terms of geographic access, that if some therapy

927
00:55:59.120 --> 00:56:01.890
is only available at the East Coast or the West Coast or in the middle of the

928
00:56:01.950 --> 00:56:05.850
country, it's a significant burden on patients and families to travel, and

