00:56:36.190 --> 00:56:40.170
studies, but they're individual studies of an in single institution, it's very

940
00:56:40.250 --> 00:56:43.970
hard to know if the same therapy is being given at each of those places.

941
00:56:44.510 --> 00:56:46.570
Because it's not just even the construct.

