01:07:14.118 --> 01:07:18.048
companies that have a finite amount of capital and are not raising any

1132
01:07:18.078 --> 01:07:21.638
revenue, which means when the money's gone, the money's gone, and if they don't

1133
01:07:21.678 --> 01:07:24.678
