1134
01:07:25.198 --> 01:07:27.758
And I think that that's very important because these companies have different

1135
01:07:27.798 --> 01:07:29.258
priority structures and levels of

1136
01:07:29.318 --> 01:07:32.374
resourcing.And it has

1137
01:07:32.414 --> 01:07:36.324
been a rough five years for the biopharmaceutical

1138
01:07:36.394 --> 01:07:40.354
