1158
01:08:52.315 --> 01:08:54.894
remarkable. One is that we've seen a string of commercial failures.

1159
01:08:54.934 --> 01:08:57.674
So we've gotten drugs approved, but they haven't delivered on their promise.

1160
01:08:57.704 --> 01:09:00.945
And what that's meant is that investors are now asking for a clear-eyed and

1161
01:09:00.974 --> 01:09:04.294
defensible quantification of treatment-addressable markets prior to

1162
01:09:04.334 --> 01:09:08.214
