1171
01:09:36.974 --> 01:09:40.554
So we've seen this host of new opportunities with far larger treatment-addressable

1172
01:09:40.655 --> 01:09:44.334
markets, with far less competition, less risk, and much, much

1173
01:09:44.344 --> 01:09:48.254
