01:10:07.114 --> 01:10:11.094
And of course, we're seeing ADCs, T-cell engagers, not just for oncology,

1180
01:10:11.194 --> 01:10:14.834
but for autoimmune diseases. And any of you who've watched a sports game

1181
01:10:14.874 --> 01:10:18.794
recently, like my daughter can sing the Skyrizi jingle, and I'm sure most

