01:29:14.274 --> 01:29:18.244
But finding a champion within a company and repeatedly reminding

1505
01:29:18.274 --> 01:29:21.614
them there's an opportunity here, or maybe even, and

1506
01:29:21.694 --> 01:29:25.634
I've tried this myself, which is calling companies

